::Battera::

"I know my friend will bring no harm to anyone.  He wishes to bring 
about peace as the Matrix has instructed him to do. He and the others 
with him will cooperate.  The ones that I can not tell for sure are 
the Alliance leaders and Megatron. We will be there ti help insure 
that the talks are peacefull." She walked to a chair and sat down. 
"As I said, I will sty here until the talks are over. If something 
happens, then kill me for vengance." SHe looked down.  She hoped that 
this maximal might try to understand what she was attemping to do. 
But then again, with all the hatred that this maximal had for Preds, 
it would take a miracle for this one to start to even try.
